                        </p>

                        <p>
                            This approach not only simplifies budgeting but also
                            provides transparency in pricing.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="faq">
                    <button class="faq-question"
                        >How long does it take to translate a document?</button
                    >
